'''弗加达岛'''（{{lang-hr|Vrgada}}，{{IPA-sh|vř̩ɡaːda|hr}}）是位于[[克罗地亚|克罗地亚]][[亚得里亚海|亚得里亚海]]沿岸的岛屿，位于[[扎達爾|扎達爾]]和[[希贝尼克|希贝尼克]]之间，[[穆泰爾島|穆泰尔西北群岛]]和[[比奥格勒纳莫鲁|比奥格勒纳莫鲁南部群岛]]之间，距离大陆{{convert|2.5|nmi|km}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pakostane.hr/vrgada_HR.php |title=Vrgada on pakostane.hr |access-date=2006-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060716090201/http://www.pakostane.hr/vrgada_HR.php |archive-date=2006-07-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，面积{{convert|3.7|km2|0}}<ref name="Duplancic-Cala-Ujevic">{{cite journal |url=https://hrcak.srce.hr/9636 |title=Coastline lengths and areas of islands in the Croatian part of the Adriatic Sea determined from the topographic maps at the scale of 1 : 25000 |journal=Geoadria |location=Zadar |volume=9 |issue=1 |pages=5–32 |date=June 2004 |last1=Duplančić Leder |first1=Tea |last2=Ujević |first2=Tin |last3=Čala |first3=Mendi |doi=10.15291/geoadria.127 |format=PDF |accessdate=2019-12-13 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021090159/https://hrcak.srce.hr/9636 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="peljar">{{cite web |title=VRGADA :: peljar.cvs.hr |url=http://peljar.cvs.hr/show_place_info.php?id=111 |website=peljar.cvs.hr |accessdate=2020-07-05 |archive-date=2012-05-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67sMltHcO?url=http://peljar.cvs.hr/show_place_info.php?id=111 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，人口249<ref name="yearbook">{{Croatia Yearbook 2015|page=47}}</ref>。岛上唯一的村镇也较弗加达<ref name="HE">{{cite encyclopedia|url=http://www.enciklopedija.hr/natuknica.aspx?ID=65469|title=Vrgada|encyclopedia=Croatian Encyclopedia|publisher=Miroslav Krleža Institute of Lexicography|language=hr|accessdate=2019-12-13|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413163947/https://www.enciklopedija.hr/natuknica.aspx?id=65469|dead-url=no}}</ref>，四周被松树林环抱<ref name="peljar"/><ref>{{cite web |title=Vrgada |url=http://www.pakostane.info/vrgada.php |website=pakostane.net/ |accessdate=2020-07-05 |archive-date=2006-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060830094507/http://www.pakostane.info/vrgada.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。岛上的主要工业为农业和捕鱼业<ref name="peljar"/>。东北方的海岸有几个小海湾<ref name="peljar"/>。

